  - m_Id: 15104418490204160
    m_Localized: Breaking Wooden Boxes and Cages
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 15104340442595328
    m_Localized: Build Bridges
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 15104457342042112
    m_Localized: Healing
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 15107973724880896
    m_Localized: Jump onto wooden crates and cages to break them. Metal crates are
      tougher and you'll need the claws to destroy them.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 15108181124825088
    m_Localized: Push the crates onto the marked spots to activate bridges. When
      a crate is placed correctly it will change color.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 15108356652253184
    m_Localized: Press H to heal yourself and recover health when injured.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
